NOKIA 5110 GAME CONSOLE POR
by Nick Frangos (2019)

[X] 1. NOKIA 5110 LCD DRIVER
[X] 	a. Display commands
[X] 	b. Draw pixel
[X] 	c. Fill Screen
[X] 	d. Draw chkrbrd
[X] 	e. Draw chars
[X] 	f. Build display map data structure
[X] 	g. Draw lines
[X] 	h. Draw rectangles
[ ] 	i. Store char map in EEPROM

[ ] 2. AVR Timer Driver
[ ] 	a. Use timer ISR to call function pointer

[ ] 3. Snake Game
[X] 	a. Build snake body data-structure
[X] 	b. Add and delete segments
[X] 	c. Grow and move body
[X] 	d. Reset upon contacting body segment or OoB
[X] 	e. Change direction
[ ] 	f. Place apple in random location
[ ] 	g. User input from push-button GPIO
[ ] 	h. Use timer to update game status
[ ] 	i. Generate menu system
[ ] 	i. Debug why game freezes after ~2mins of uptime - possible memory leak

